All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Geometry, GeometryCollection, HitTest, MPointCollection, MZPointCollection, PointApplicatorUser, PointCollection
public class MZBasePointsArray
extends MBasePointsArray
implements MZPointCollection

A standard implementation of Points that stores Point(s) within a pair of coordinate arrays, a measured value array, and a Z array.
